verbose_text: After treatment with folic acid at 5 mg/daily for 12 weeks, the new plasma homocysteine levels did not show any significant difference (p = 0.38) between the Buerger 's disease group (14.6 +/- 4.5 Mm/L) and atherosclerosis group (13.9 +/- 4.7), but it was found to besignificantly higher in both groups when compared to the healthy group (10.7 +/- 3.9, p < 0.05).
